{"tid":2090294,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得就算藍絲黑警去到英國 都唔驚","createTime":"2020-07-02T05:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T06:59:16.000Z","uid":89538,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4d8cc4fe73678bfadd5b146eed830f2e4020c171","tid":2090294,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"首先 一堆老屎忽離開左香港 自然會係上層空番d職位出黎 咁年青人先有得上流（唔排除會比大陸人搶）<br />\n<br />\n第二 佢地班撚樣英文咁廢（尤其d狗）就算去到英國都唔荒生活得好<br />\n<br />\n第三 仲可以帶走資金資產 學李光耀話齊 廿萬精英（舊時代老屎忽）離開 可以攤渙香港行政經濟<br />\n呢樣係我地後生做唔到<br />\n<br />\n所以大家唔洗太擔心 <br />\n當然可以篤灰等佢留係香港享受中國人榮耀就當然最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 愛國愛黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31cd0dbad330cfdd4be2e68e6145d50ece55e0f7","tid":2090294,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:50:59.000Z","msg":"最緊要有錢，講完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：文明社會"},{"pid":"6173608c6a849f710a25cc167b15d43234cfadb4","tid":2090294,"uid":10094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:59:16.000Z","msg":"走一個香港少一個藍絲唔無仲好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}